{
  "stem": "22685.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was not like in America, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- they called you up to the Torah, you read the Torah, and then it was a Kiddush.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at home, was some of a few family members, some family member with another little reception.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But nothing big, nothing elaborate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, typical, it was-- depends on my age, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, I had to comply with certain rules.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was told to do, I had to do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was older, a little, we compromised.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, we always had the Shabbos meal, the Shabbos-- everybody was at the Shabbos dinner.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after dinner, it depends on what age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the beginning, we were going to visit relatives, or they came to visit us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after a while, when I was older, I already was going to my own friends for-- to visit or to whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course we knew-- I was always very interested in politics.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were reading, we were listening, and we had a free press, and-- and we knew exactly what was going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- I-- we had a three-storey building that we lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each of my uncles had a quarter, like we had the main floor, my uncle had the top floor, and the other corner, the other uncle had the main floor, and the aunt with the children.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were 12 all together, each one had three children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had disagreements, in a sense, that some of the [NON-ENGLISH], which is the Gentiles, they attacked us, but since we were a group of 12.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We waited for them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They never came twice to our street anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On top of it, in Poland, was an organization-- a Fascist organization-- which I'll discuss-- the initials ND, Index.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
